#! /usr/local/bin/stoical
% 04/24/02 - Jonathan Moore Liles.
% Library to approximate Rob Spruit's Cryptic Constructs, in STOICAL.

'cryptic branch

cryptic< definitions

'?{	: () if{	exec ; immediate
'}{	: () }else{	exec ; immediate
'?}	: () }until  	exec ; immediate
'?}{	: () }while{	exec ; immediate

'xx{	: () loop{	exec ; immediate

> definitions

cryptic<

;f

Translations:

Traditional			Cryptic
-------
if{ ... }			?{ ... }
if{ ... }else{ ... }		?{ ... }{ ... }

{ ... }until			{ ... ?}
{ ... }while{ ... } 		{ ... ?}{ ... }

n n loop{ ... }			xx{	}

